    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>骗子骰子 是一款以虚张声势为主题的roguelike游戏，玩家需要利用隐藏的骰子、大胆的赌注以及通过欺骗和推理智胜对手。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/a6360d44e3efc4bf8c0fb132932906b2.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/a6360d44e3efc4bf8c0fb132932906b2.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/a6360d44e3efc4bf8c0fb132932906b2.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欺骗求生</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >智胜虚张声势，坚持到底，赢得自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/7d7d1e831304ba97804019ad65fc8780.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/7d7d1e831304ba97804019ad65fc8780.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/7d7d1e831304ba97804019ad65fc8780.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/888dc5681bc7c26b6548cd31441da8a5.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/888dc5681bc7c26b6548cd31441da8a5.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/888dc5681bc7c26b6548cd31441da8a5.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掷骰求生</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次掷骰都是一场赌博，每一轮都是一场心理游戏。你的直觉会指引你走向胜利吗？                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/5eb47a5831d5136f7213945eb15d0a1f.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/5eb47a5831d5136f7213945eb15d0a1f.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/5eb47a5831d5136f7213945eb15d0a1f.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >命运之战 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两位玩家，十二个骰子，以及一个黑暗的真相：最终只有一人能活下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/8d9764787b16311d7d02e6f552d3b3c1.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/8d9764787b16311d7d02e6f552d3b3c1.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/8d9764787b16311d7d02e6f552d3b3c1.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逃离阴影</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会成为幸存者，还是会被黑暗吞噬？</p>",
